improvements (such as in the Aeronautics and Aviation field, Automotive
fields and most others). Modern society tends to rely on such
incremental improvements. Theoretical Physicists tend to see such approaches
as being somewhat blind attempts to create advanced concepts and devices,
where we feel that a good understanding of the logic and facts might enable
an entirely NEW perspective regarding any subject. You may notice this
