For comparison, a C-4 Corvette, a rather aerodynamic car, has an
aerodynamic drag of about 117 pounds and a tire drag of about 48
pounds at 60 mph, for a total vehicle Drag of 165 pounds.  So the
numbers we are using are very optimistic!<p>

